{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/BARRENWALKING.gif?t=1738761750\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/Group_95_2_.png?t=1738761750\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Kaodi</i> is a brief tale about the scars that war leaves on both the world and the heart. After playing a pivotal role in the victory over the Republic of Shan, Barren must journey home on a path laden with guilt, trauma, doubts, broken friendships, and fractured loyalties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with a wide array of characters, each offering a fresh perspective on the devastation of war: stories of loss, dignity, forgiveness\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The experience is enriched by a beautiful art style, blending traditional pixel art with 3D modeling techniques and effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/INNER_WORLD.png?t=1738761750\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through the <i>Inner World</i>, you\u2019ll navigate Barren's deepest thoughts. Reflect on them or interact with other NPCs to uncover powerful testimonies, complete small quests, and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/Inner.gif?t=1738761750\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325570/extras/COMBAT___PLATFORMS.png?t=1738761750\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even though the war is over, Barren will be forced to duel his way through 